1
00:01:02,660 --> 00:01:03,660
Hmph.

2
00:01:08,830 --> 00:01:09,750
No rush.

3
00:01:10,450 --> 00:01:13,410
The best is yet to come.

4
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:42,450
This has been passed down in our Yaowang Valley.

5
00:01:42,450 --> 00:01:43,700
Ever since I joined the valley and became an apprentice,

6
00:01:43,700 --> 00:01:45,539
this pattern has been on the medicine chest.

7
00:01:45,539 --> 00:01:47,400
I don't know what it means either.

8
00:01:49,039 --> 00:01:50,160
My master said

9
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:52,160
this is the genesis mark of our valley,

10
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:54,090
passed down for hundreds of years.

11
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,910
Drink the nourishing soup in the morning.

12
00:02:05,910 --> 00:02:07,750
Do not touch cold water before bed.

13
00:02:07,750 --> 00:02:08,870
Your condition has just stabilized.

14
00:02:08,870 --> 00:02:10,470
You can't be careless again.

15
00:02:11,870 --> 00:02:13,160
Rest well.

16
00:02:18,660 --> 00:02:20,790
It's rare to have such peaceful times.

17
00:02:26,500 --> 00:02:27,040
General.

18
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,950
Someone from the Prime Minister's residence delivered an urgent letter,

19
00:02:28,950 --> 00:02:31,040
along with the wound medicine you usually use

20
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:33,440
and a fox fur coat for the cold at the border.

21
00:02:33,450 --> 00:02:35,410
Prime Minister Qin specifically instructed,

22
00:02:35,410 --> 00:02:36,750
saying the border is bitterly cold,

23
00:02:36,750 --> 00:02:38,680
and you must take care of yourself.

24
00:02:41,790 --> 00:02:42,540
Prime Minister Qin

25
00:02:42,540 --> 00:02:44,070
has always looked after me.

26
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:46,100
Since my father passed away,

27
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:48,650
I have relied much on his protection at court.

28
00:02:53,040 --> 00:02:53,579
General.

29
00:02:53,579 --> 00:02:54,950
Urgent report from the border.

30
00:02:54,950 --> 00:02:56,040
The Xiongnu are invading in full force,

31
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:57,290
having breached three cities.

32
00:02:57,290 --> 00:03:01,150
The commander urgently summons you to ride to their aid immediately.

33
00:03:01,910 --> 00:03:03,160
Prepare the horses and rally the troops.

34
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,500
We leave in half an hour.

35
00:03:05,580 --> 00:03:06,790
The border is dangerous.

36
00:03:06,790 --> 00:03:09,330
And that woman of unknown origin is eyeing you like prey.

37
00:03:09,330 --> 00:03:11,790
I can't rest easy leaving you in the capital.

38
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:12,870
Besides, I always feel that

39
00:03:12,870 --> 00:03:14,400
clues to your true identity

40
00:03:14,410 --> 00:03:16,070
might be hidden at the border.

41
00:03:16,250 --> 00:03:17,750
Do you want to come with me?

42
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:19,260
I will protect you.

43
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:24,410
Sister.

44
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,660
Trying to flee to the border to avoid trouble?

45
00:03:26,660 --> 00:03:28,410
Stop deceiving yourself.

46
00:03:28,660 --> 00:03:30,620
Your forgotten past

47
00:03:30,620 --> 00:03:32,250
is not what you think.

48
00:03:32,329 --> 00:03:34,579
In your final moments back then,

49
00:03:34,579 --> 00:03:36,540
it was me you leaned on.

50
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:48,290
Sister.

51
00:03:48,829 --> 00:03:49,829
Ying.

52
00:03:50,660 --> 00:03:51,660
Don't cry.

53
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:54,160
Live well.

54
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:03,950
Who exactly are you?

55
00:04:03,950 --> 00:04:05,150
What did you do to her?

56
00:04:05,660 --> 00:04:06,830
You want to know?

57
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,690
Then take her to the border.

58
00:04:08,910 --> 00:04:09,500
There,

59
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:12,330
lie all the answers to her identity.

60
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:22,760
We must cut the weeds and dig up the roots.

61
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:29,620
I am willing to stake my position as Grand Commandant

62
00:04:29,620 --> 00:04:31,540
and a lifetime of honor as a guarantee.

63
00:04:31,540 --> 00:04:33,870
Xie Lin has absolutely no intention of treason.

64
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:35,620
His son Jingchen is only ten years old

65
00:04:35,620 --> 00:04:36,500
and uninvolved in military affairs.

66
00:04:36,500 --> 00:04:38,159
I beg Your Majesty to spare him the death penalty,

67
00:04:38,159 --> 00:04:39,080
strip his title, and place him under house arrest.

68
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:41,750
If it is proven in the future that Xie Jingchen harbors treasonous thoughts,

69
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:43,409
I am willing to suffer the same punishment.

70
00:04:43,409 --> 00:04:44,210
Your Majesty.

71
00:04:44,290 --> 00:04:45,790
Grand Commandant Lin is absolutely right.

72
00:04:45,790 --> 00:04:47,750
General Xie's reputation for loyalty and bravery is known to all.

73
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:49,200
There is no solid proof of his treason yet.

74
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:50,500
If his entire family is executed rashly,

75
00:04:50,500 --> 00:04:52,790
it will surely chill the hearts of hundreds of thousands of soldiers at the border.

76
00:04:52,790 --> 00:04:54,000
Xie Jingchen is young and innocent.

77
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,370
You may follow Grand Commandant Lin's advice,

78
00:04:55,370 --> 00:04:56,200
spare him from death,

79
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:58,450
and decide his fate after the truth is found out.
